                     <lb/><l><gap quantity="1" unit="char" reason="illegible"/>or,<unclear>a</unclear>ll in <unclear>a</unclear>ll,<unclear>s</unclear>he h<unclear>a</unclear><subst><del rend="overtyped">d</del><add place="superimposed">s</add></subst> do<unclear>n</unclear>e</l>
                     <lb/><l>(<gap quantity="1" unit="char" reason="illegible"/>ur ugly looks are our <unclear>d</unclear>eed)</l>
